reviewText: This was basically just 14 guys jacking off..but with no flavor or style of anything new. How can you get off by dry humping a blanket or your mattress?? And many of it just got over-played. I actually fell asleep while watching this. I woke up and I was on guy 14, but I thought that I was on guy 5?? That disturbs me because I spent a good deal amount of money on this movie. The guy on the cover was descent looking, but the hottest guy was number 1. He was really going to town in the woodshop. haha. But, don't bother buying...I fell asleep, and I'm sure you will too.
